{%- liquid
  assign mv_names = "Charlotte J.,Isabella E.,George B.,Sophie M.,Priya R.,Thomas B.,Olivia S.,James P.,Emma L.,Lucy A.,Nathan R.,Amelia C.,Freya H.,Oliver T.,Daniel K.,Hannah W.,Megan F.,Ryan D.,Chloe V.,Adam S.,Grace N.,Leo M.,Ben C.,Zoe P.,Harry L.,Ella J.,Sam W.,Ruth A.,Mark T.,Fiona G.,Paul R.,Karen D.,Sarah H.,Jack M.,Alice B.,Henry C.,Niamh O.,William T.,Holly S.,Aaron P.,Maya K.,Ethan R.,Poppy L.,Joseph N.,Ava M.,Lewis G.,Isla F.,Connor B." | split: ","
  assign mv_dates = "March 2026,February 2026,January 2026,December 2025,November 2025,October 2025,September 2025,August 2025,July 2025,June 2025,May 2025,April 2025" | split: ","
  assign q5 = "The finish adds a quiet, elegant touch and the shade gives a warm evening glow.|Exactly the light I wanted above my console table and it looks far more expensive than it was.|A simple change that made the bedroom feel considered. It sits beautifully next to framed art.|Installation was genuinely tool-free. I stuck them either side of the bed and they have not moved.|The brass finish is gorgeous and feels far from cheap. Guests always ask where they are from.|Battery life is better than expected and recharging is simple. Perfect for a rented flat.|Transformed a dark corner of the living room. Honestly looks like a proper hard-wired fitting.|The set of two was ideal for our alcoves. Simple, classy and no electrician needed.|Soft, flattering glow and the shade quality is lovely. Already planning a pair for the bedroom.|Easy to reposition until the spacing looked right. So pleased with how finished the wall feels.|Warm light without any harsh glare, and the remote makes it effortless in the evenings.|Beautiful quality for the price. They look like a designer piece in our hallway.|Perfect bedside lighting. The dimmable warm glow is exactly what we hoped for.|Looks stunning either side of the mirror and took five minutes to put up.|Such a clever idea: all the charm of a sconce with none of the wiring hassle.|The light is warm and cosy, ideal for winding down at the end of the day.|Sturdier than I expected and the shade feels premium. Very happy with the purchase.|Added instant character to a plain hallway. Neighbours have already asked about them.|Charging lasts ages and the light is the perfect warmth. Could not be happier.|Elegant, understated and beautifully made. Exactly the finishing touch the room needed.|No drilling, no mess, and they look completely permanent on the wall.|The remote and timer are so handy. They come on softly every evening like clockwork.|Gorgeous in our bedroom. The glow is flattering and calm, never clinical.|I was nervous about stick-on lights but these feel solid and look high-end.|Brightened up the stairway perfectly. The warm tone makes the whole space feel inviting.|Lovely craftsmanship and a really cosy light. Would happily buy another set.|They frame the mirror beautifully and the light is perfect for getting ready.|So easy that I did the whole thing myself in minutes. Looks fantastic.|The shade diffuses the light beautifully: soft, warm and never glary.|Genuinely impressed by the quality. Feels like a luxury fitting at a fair price." | split: "|"
  assign q4 = "Lovely warm light and an elegant shape. Slightly smaller than I pictured, but great in the hallway.|Great for a cosy evening layer. I would love a slightly longer remote range, but happy overall.|Looks high-end and was simple to fit. Took off a star as I would like one brighter setting.|Really pleased with these. Would have liked a paper wall template included for spacing.|Elegant and well made. The shade is a touch more cream than white in person.|Good quality and easy setup. The charging cable is a little short but not a deal breaker.|Lovely glow and very easy to live with. A second brightness level would make it perfect.|Smart-looking sconces. Pairing the remote took a moment but it works reliably now.|Really nice light and finish. I just wish the battery indicator was a bit clearer.|Looks great on the wall. Took a little patience to get both perfectly level.|Warm and cosy as described. Would have liked a slightly bigger shade for my space.|Happy with these overall: stylish and practical for a rental.|Good value and they look lovely lit. The off setting could be easier to find on the remote.|Nicely made and easy to fit. A warmer bulb option would have been the cherry on top.|Pleased with the look. Charging every few weeks is fine but worth knowing in advance.|Solid little lights with a lovely glow. Instructions could be a little more detailed.|They look far pricier than they are. Only minor niggle is the remote feels a bit light.|Great addition to the bedroom. Took one star off only because delivery took a little while." | split: "|"
  assign q3 = "Nice light, though the remote range is shorter than I would like across a big room.|Good value and easy to set up. The printed instructions were a little basic.|Pretty much as expected. Slightly smaller than they looked in the photos.|Warm glow is lovely; I just wish the battery lasted a bit longer between charges.|They look great on the wall. The adhesive needed a firmer press than I expected to hold.|Decent lights for the price. The shade is nice but a little thinner than I imagined.|Happy enough: they do the job, though I expected a slightly brighter output.|Look good but took some fiddling to get the spacing even. Fine once up.|The light is pleasant. I wish the remote was backlit for using in the dark.|Reasonable quality. Recharging more often than I hoped, but the look makes up for it." | split: "|"
  assign q2 = "The lights themselves are lovely, but delivery took nearly three weeks, longer than stated.|Happy with the sconces, however one box arrived a little dented by the courier.|Took a while to arrive and the tracking was not very clear. The product itself is great.|Product is good but shipping was slow and I had to chase an update on my order.|Lovely lights, let down only by a delayed delivery that arrived later than promised.|The sconces are great; the courier just left them outside in the rain, which was a shame." | split: "|"
  assign q1 = "Delivery was much slower than I expected, almost a month. The lamps are lovely now they are finally up.|Courier left it with a neighbour without telling me. Frustrating shipping, though the product is good.|Waited far too long for dispatch and updates were slow. The lights are nice, the delivery was not.|Shipping took ages and tracking barely worked. Happy with the sconces once they eventually arrived." | split: "|"
  assign n5 = 150
  assign n4 = 90
  assign n3 = 18
  assign n2 = 8
  assign n1 = 4
  assign mv_total = n5 | plus: n4 | plus: n3 | plus: n2 | plus: n1
  assign mv_modal_id = 'MeaveReviews-' | append: section.id
-%}

<section class="meave-reviews">
  <div class="meave-reviews__inner">
    <div class="meave-reviews__head">
      <p class="meave-reviews__eyebrow">Reviews</p>
      {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
        <h2>{{ section.settings.heading | escape }}</h2>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    {%- if section.settings.show_summary -%}
      <div class="meave-reviews__summary">
        <div class="meave-reviews__score">
          <span class="meave-reviews__scoreNum">{{ section.settings.rating_average | escape }}</span>
          <div class="meave-reviews__scoreStars" role="img" aria-label="{{ section.settings.rating_average | escape }} out of 5">
            {%- for star in (1..5) -%}
              <svg class="is-active" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2.8 14.8 8.5l6.3.9-4.6 4.4 1.1 6.3-5.6-3-5.6 3 1.1-6.3-4.6-4.4 6.3-.9L12 2.8Z"/></svg>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
          <span class="meave-reviews__scoreCount">{{ section.settings.rating_count | escape }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="meave-reviews__bars">
          {%- assign pcts = section.settings.pct_5 | append: ',' | append: section.settings.pct_4 | append: ',' | append: section.settings.pct_3 | append: ',' | append: section.settings.pct_2 | append: ',' | append: section.settings.pct_1 | split: ',' -%}
          {%- for pct in pcts -%}
            <div class="meave-reviews__bar">
              <span class="meave-reviews__barLabel">{{ 5 | minus: forloop.index0 }}</span>
              <svg class="meave-reviews__barStar" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2.8 14.8 8.5l6.3.9-4.6 4.4 1.1 6.3-5.6-3-5.6 3 1.1-6.3-4.6-4.4 6.3-.9L12 2.8Z"/></svg>
              <span class="meave-reviews__barTrack"><span class="meave-reviews__barFill" style="width: {{ pct }}%;"></span></span>
              <span class="meave-reviews__barPct">{{ pct }}%</span>
            </div>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- endif -%}

    <div class="meave-reviews__grid">
      {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
        <article class="meave-review" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
          <div class="meave-review__stars" role="img" aria-label="{{ block.settings.rating }} out of 5 stars">
            {%- for star in (1..5) -%}
              <svg class="{% if star <= block.settings.rating %}is-active{% endif %}" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M12 2.8 14.8 8.5l6.3.9-4.6 4.4 1.1 6.3-5.6-3-5.6 3 1.1-6.3-4.6-4.4 6.3-.9L12 2.8Z"/>
              </svg>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
          {%- if block.settings.quote != blank -%}
            <div class="meave-review__quote rte">{{ block.settings.quote }}</div>
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if block.settings.image != blank -%}
            <figure class="meave-review__photo">
              {{- block.settings.image
                | image_url: width: 720
                | image_tag:
                  loading: 'lazy',
                  widths: '320,480,640,720',
                  sizes: '(min-width: 990px) 360px, 86vw',
                  alt: block.settings.image_alt
              -}}
              <span class="meave-review__photoTag" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3.2"/><path d="M8 5l1.2-2h5.6L16 5"/></svg>
                Customer photo
              </span>
            </figure>
          {%- endif -%}
          {%- if block.settings.author != blank -%}
            <div class="meave-review__author">
              <span class="meave-review__avatar" aria-hidden="true">{{ block.settings.author | strip | slice: 0 | upcase }}</span>
              <span class="meave-review__who">
                <span class="meave-review__name">{{ block.settings.author | escape }}</span>
                {%- if block.settings.verified -%}
                  <span class="meave-review__verified">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="m8.5 12 2.3 2.3 4.7-4.9"/></svg>
                    Verified buyer
                  </span>
                {%- endif -%}
              </span>
            </div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </article>
      {%- endfor -%}

      {%- comment -%} Extra written reviews so the wall feels full (photos sit on the first row) {%- endcomment -%}
      {%- assign extra_count = section.settings.extra_reviews | default: 6 -%}
      {%- for i in (1..extra_count) -%}
        {%- assign nidx = forloop.index0 | plus: 6 | modulo: mv_names.size -%}
        {%- assign didx = forloop.index0 | plus: 3 | modulo: mv_dates.size -%}
        {%- assign qidx = forloop.index0 | plus: 4 | modulo: q5.size -%}
        {%- assign aname = mv_names[nidx] -%}
        <article class="meave-review meave-review--text">
          <div class="meave-review__stars" role="img" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">
            {%- for star in (1..5) -%}
              <svg class="is-active" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2.8 14.8 8.5l6.3.9-4.6 4.4 1.1 6.3-5.6-3-5.6 3 1.1-6.3-4.6-4.4 6.3-.9L12 2.8Z"/></svg>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
          <div class="meave-review__quote"><p>{{ q5[qidx] | escape }}</p></div>
          <div class="meave-review__author">
            <span class="meave-review__avatar" aria-hidden="true">{{ aname | strip | slice: 0 | upcase }}</span>
            <span class="meave-review__who">
              <span class="meave-review__name">{{ aname | escape }}</span>
              <span class="meave-review__verified">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="m8.5 12 2.3 2.3 4.7-4.9"/></svg>
                Verified buyer
              </span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </article>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>

    <div class="meave-reviews__actions">
      <button type="button" class="meave-reviews__all" data-mvrev-open aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-controls="{{ mv_modal_id }}">
        View all reviews
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mvrev-modal" id="{{ mv_modal_id }}" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Customer reviews" hidden>
    <div class="mvrev-modal__overlay" data-mvrev-close></div>
    <div class="mvrev-modal__panel" role="document">
      <div class="mvrev-modal__head">
        <div class="mvrev-modal__headTop">
          <div class="mvrev-modal__score">
            <span class="mvrev-modal__scoreNum">{{ section.settings.rating_average | escape }}</span>
            <span class="mvrev-modal__scoreStars" aria-hidden="true">
              {%- for star in (1..5) -%}
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2.8 14.8 8.5l6.3.9-4.6 4.4 1.1 6.3-5.6-3-5.6 3 1.1-6.3-4.6-4.4 6.3-.9L12 2.8Z"/></svg>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </span>
            <span class="mvrev-modal__scoreCount">{{ section.settings.rating_count | escape }}</span>
          </div>
          <button type="button" class="mvrev-modal__close" data-mvrev-close aria-label="Close reviews">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 6l12 12M18 6 6 18"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="mvrev-modal__tabs" role="tablist">
          <button type="button" class="mvrev-modal__tab is-active" data-mvrev-filter="all">All reviews</button>
          <button type="button" class="mvrev-modal__tab" data-mvrev-filter="5">5 ★</button>
          <button type="button" class="mvrev-modal__tab" data-mvrev-filter="4">4 ★</button>
          <button type="button" class="mvrev-modal__tab" data-mvrev-filter="3">3 ★</button>
          <button type="button" class="mvrev-modal__tab" data-mvrev-filter="2">2 ★</button>
          <button type="button" class="mvrev-modal__tab" data-mvrev-filter="1">1 ★</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ul class="mvrev-modal__list" data-mvrev-list>
        {%- assign rating_list = "5,4,3,2,1" | split: "," -%}
        {%- assign count_list = "150,90,18,8,4" | split: "," -%}
        {%- assign g = 0 -%}
        {%- for ridx in (0..4) -%}
          {%- assign rv = rating_list[ridx] -%}
          {%- assign cv = count_list[ridx] | plus: 0 -%}
          {%- liquid
            case rv
              when "5"
                assign qpool = q5
                assign gold = "★★★★★"
                assign offstars = ""
              when "4"
                assign qpool = q4
                assign gold = "★★★★"
                assign offstars = "☆"
              when "3"
                assign qpool = q3
                assign gold = "★★★"
                assign offstars = "☆☆"
              when "2"
                assign qpool = q2
                assign gold = "★★"
                assign offstars = "☆☆☆"
              when "1"
                assign qpool = q1
                assign gold = "★"
                assign offstars = "☆☆☆☆"
            endcase
          -%}
          {%- for i in (1..cv) -%}
            {%- assign qi = forloop.index0 | modulo: qpool.size -%}
            {%- assign nidx = g | modulo: mv_names.size -%}
            {%- assign didx = g | modulo: mv_dates.size -%}
            {%- assign g = g | plus: 1 -%}
            {%- assign aname = mv_names[nidx] -%}
            <li class="mvrev-item" data-rating="{{ rv }}">
              <div class="mvrev-item__top">
                <span class="mvrev-item__avatar" aria-hidden="true">{{ aname | strip | slice: 0 | upcase }}</span>
                <span class="mvrev-item__who">
                  <span class="mvrev-item__name">{{ aname | escape }}</span>
                  <span class="mvrev-item__verified">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="m8.5 12 2.3 2.3 4.7-4.9"/></svg>
                    Verified buyer
                  </span>
                </span>
                <span class="mvrev-item__date">{{ mv_dates[didx] | escape }}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mvrev-item__stars" role="img" aria-label="{{ rv }} out of 5"><span class="on">{{ gold }}</span><span class="off">{{ offstars }}</span></div>
              <p class="mvrev-item__text">{{ qpool[qi] | escape }}</p>
            </li>
          {%- endfor -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  (function () {
    var root = document.getElementById('{{ mv_modal_id }}');
    if (!root) return;
    var section = root.closest('.shopify-section') || document;
    var openers = section.querySelectorAll('[data-mvrev-open]');
    var closers = root.querySelectorAll('[data-mvrev-close]');
    var tabs = root.querySelectorAll('[data-mvrev-filter]');
    var items = root.querySelectorAll('.mvrev-item');
    var list = root.querySelector('[data-mvrev-list]');

    function open() {
      if (root.parentNode !== document.body) {
        document.body.appendChild(root);
      }
      root.hidden = false;
      document.documentElement.style.overflow = 'hidden';
      document.body.classList.add('mvrev-open');
      requestAnimationFrame(function () { root.classList.add('is-open'); });
    }
    function close() {
      root.classList.remove('is-open');
      document.documentElement.style.overflow = '';
      document.body.classList.remove('mvrev-open');
      setTimeout(function () { root.hidden = true; }, 260);
    }
    function filter(val) {
      items.forEach(function (it) {
        it.style.display = (val === 'all' || it.getAttribute('data-rating') === val) ? '' : 'none';
      });
      if (list) list.scrollTop = 0;
    }

    openers.forEach(function (b) { b.addEventListener('click', open); });
    closers.forEach(function (b) { b.addEventListener('click', close); });
    tabs.forEach(function (t) {
      t.addEventListener('click', function () {
        tabs.forEach(function (x) { x.classList.remove('is-active'); });
        t.classList.add('is-active');
        filter(t.getAttribute('data-mvrev-filter'));
      });
    });
    document.addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
      if (e.key === 'Escape' && !root.hidden) close();
    });
  })();
</script>

{% stylesheet %}
  .meave-reviews {
    padding: 96px 20px;
    background: #fff;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .meave-reviews__inner {
    max-width: 1120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .meave-reviews__head {
    margin: 0 auto 44px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .meave-reviews__eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: #6e6e73;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: .16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .meave-reviews h2 {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -.025em;
    line-height: 1.08;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  /* Aggregate rating summary */
  .meave-reviews__summary {
    display: grid;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 44px;
    padding: 28px 34px;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 34px;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 0.5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .05), 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, .03), 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, .05);
  }

  .meave-reviews__score {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding-right: 34px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .08);
  }

  .meave-reviews__scoreNum {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -.03em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .meave-reviews__scoreStars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .meave-reviews__scoreStars svg {
    width: 16px;
    color: #ffb400;
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  .meave-reviews__scoreCount {
    color: #6e6e73;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 400;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .meave-reviews__bars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 7px;
  }

  .meave-reviews__bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .meave-reviews__barLabel {
    width: 10px;
    color: #6e6e73;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .meave-reviews__barStar {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    color: #c7c7cc;
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  .meave-reviews__barTrack {
    position: relative;
    flex: 1 1 auto;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 99px;
    background: #e7e7eb;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .meave-reviews__barFill {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0 auto 0 0;
    border-radius: 99px;
    background: #ffb400;
  }

  .meave-reviews__barPct {
    width: 34px;
    color: #6e6e73;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-align: right;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .meave-reviews__grid {
    display: grid;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 18px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .meave-review {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 28px 28px 24px;
    border-radius: 18px;
    background: #fff;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: left;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 0.5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .05), 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, .03), 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, .05);
    transition: transform .4s cubic-bezier(.22, 1, .36, 1), box-shadow .4s cubic-bezier(.22, 1, .36, 1);
  }

  .meave-review:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 0.5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .05), 0 18px 44px rgba(0, 0, 0, .09);
  }

  .meave-review__stars {
    display: flex;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .meave-review__stars svg {
    width: 15px;
    color: #d8d8dd;
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  .meave-review__stars svg.is-active {
    color: #ffb400;
  }

  .meave-review__quote {
    position: relative;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    letter-spacing: -.01em;
    flex: 1 1 auto;
  }

  .meave-review__quote p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .meave-review__photo {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 20px 0 0;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: #f5f5f7;
  }

  .meave-review__photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform .7s cubic-bezier(.22, 1, .36, 1);
  }

  .meave-review:hover .meave-review__photo img {
    transform: scale(1.04);
  }

  .meave-review__photoTag {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 9px;
    left: 9px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 4px 9px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, .5);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .95);
    font-size: 10.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: .01em;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }

  .meave-review__photoTag svg {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
  }

  .meave-review__author {
    display: flex;
    margin-top: 22px;
    padding-top: 18px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .07);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .meave-review__avatar {
    display: grid;
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #f0f0f3;
    color: #6e6e73;
    place-items: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .meave-review__who {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .meave-review__name {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -.01em;
    color: #1d1d1f;
  }

  .meave-review__verified {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    color: #0071e3;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .meave-review__verified svg {
    width: 13px;
    height: 13px;
    color: #0071e3;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    /* Swipeable carousel keeps reviews compact on phones/tablets */
    .meave-reviews__grid {
      display: flex;
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin: 0 -20px;
      padding: 4px 20px 12px;
      gap: 14px;
      grid-template-columns: none;
      scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }

    .meave-reviews__grid::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }

    .meave-review {
      flex: 0 0 84%;
      scroll-snap-align: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .meave-reviews__summary {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 22px;
      padding: 26px 24px;
    }

    .meave-reviews__score {
      padding: 0 0 22px;
      border-right: 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .08);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .meave-reviews {
      padding: 64px 16px;
    }

    .meave-reviews__head {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .meave-reviews__summary {
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .meave-reviews__grid {
      margin: 0 -16px;
      padding: 4px 16px 12px;
    }

    .meave-review {
      flex-basis: 86%;
      padding: 30px 26px 26px;
    }
  }

  /* Read-all button */
  .meave-reviews__actions {
    margin-top: 36px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .meave-reviews__all {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 9px;
    padding: 13px 26px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #fff;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -.01em;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 0.5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .12), 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, .04);
    transition: transform .3s cubic-bezier(.22, 1, .36, 1), box-shadow .3s ease;
  }

  .meave-reviews__all svg {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    color: #0071e3;
  }

  .meave-reviews__all:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 0.5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .14), 0 12px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, .10);
  }

  /* Modal */
  .mvrev-modal[hidden] {
    display: none;
  }

  .mvrev-modal {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 9999;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0 12px 12px;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, .4);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity .26s ease;
  }

  /* Blur the page content behind the modal (reliable fallback for backdrop-filter) */
  body.mvrev-open > *:not(.mvrev-modal):not(script):not(style) {
    filter: blur(7px);
    transition: filter .3s ease;
  }

  .mvrev-modal.is-open .mvrev-modal__overlay {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__panel {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 720px;
    max-height: 88vh;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 24px;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: transform .3s cubic-bezier(.22, 1, .36, 1), opacity .26s ease;
  }

  .mvrev-modal.is-open .mvrev-modal__panel {
    transform: translateY(0);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  @media (min-width: 700px) {
    .mvrev-modal {
      align-items: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .mvrev-modal__panel {
      border-radius: 24px;
      max-height: 84vh;
    }
  }

  .mvrev-modal__head {
    padding: 24px 26px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .08);
  }

  .mvrev-modal__headTop {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__score {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 4px 12px;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__scoreNum {
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -.03em;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__scoreStars {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__scoreStars svg {
    width: 16px;
    color: #ffb400;
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__scoreCount {
    width: 100%;
    color: #6e6e73;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__close {
    display: grid;
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    flex: 0 0 38px;
    place-items: center;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #f0f0f3;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background .2s ease;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__close:hover {
    background: #e5e5ea;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__close svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 18px;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__tabs::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__tab {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 8px 15px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #f0f0f3;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    white-space: nowrap;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background .2s ease, color .2s ease;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__tab span {
    color: #86868b;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__tab.is-active {
    background: #0071e3;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .mvrev-modal__tab.is-active span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .75);
  }

  .mvrev-modal__list {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 8px 26px 26px;
    list-style: none;
    overflow-y: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }

  .mvrev-item {
    padding: 22px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .07);
  }

  .mvrev-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
  }

  .mvrev-item__top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 11px;
  }

  .mvrev-item__avatar {
    display: grid;
    width: 34px;
    height: 34px;
    flex: 0 0 34px;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #f0f0f3;
    color: #6e6e73;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .mvrev-item__who {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    flex: 1 1 auto;
  }

  .mvrev-item__name {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1d1d1f;
  }

  .mvrev-item__verified {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    color: #0071e3;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .mvrev-item__verified svg {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    color: #0071e3;
  }

  .mvrev-item__date {
    color: #86868b;
    font-size: 12px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .mvrev-item__stars {
    margin: 12px 0 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .mvrev-item__stars .on {
    color: #ffb400;
  }

  .mvrev-item__stars .off {
    color: #d8d8dd;
  }

  .mvrev-item__text {
    margin: 0;
    color: #3a3a3c;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
{% endstylesheet %}

